OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy with scattered showers
OL,6,Fat first, these tending to become more
OL,7,Fconfined towards the east into the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Some bright or sunny spells
OL,9,Fat times, with winds gradually easing
OL,10,Flater. Temperatures near average.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBecoming generally dry with
OL,13,Fsome clear spells, but cloud
OL,14,Fthickening from the west after
OL,15,Fmidnight, bringing some patchy rain
OL,16,Fand drizzle eastwards later in the
OL,17,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
